  "title": "Pan Seared Turkish Pak Choi Imam Bayildi",
  "description": "A Whole30 friendly Turkish dish featuring pak choi, sauteed in a buttery and crunchy style, perfect for brunch, served in an earthenware bowl in the form of Imam Bayildi.",
