  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Rinse the pak choi heads and separate the leaves.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium heat and saute the garlic and onion until softened.",
    "Add the tomato paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the pak choi leaves and cook until wilted, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the pak choi mixture to an earthenware bowl and drizzle with lemon juice and ghee.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional lemon wedges if desired."
